rl.photoviewer.model

Class PVModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • rl.photoviewer.model.PVModel

  • public class PVModel
extends java.util.Observable
    Facade which provides access to the complete state of the photo viewer. The state is defined by a selected photo and an ordered collection of metadata for all photos in the directory of the selected photo.
    Author:
    Ruediger Lunde
